    "(92) conducted a systematic review and metaanalysis to evaluate ChatGPT's accuracy in medical and dental fields.",
    "Although ChatGPT's accuracy ranged from 18.3% to 100% across different studies, it generally performed better than chance, suggesting its potential as a research tool in dentistry and medicine.",
